#: ../../../release_details/9.4/disable-sdl2-by-default.md:1
msgid "SDL2 usage is now disabled by default"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/disable-sdl2-by-default.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK has now deprecated the use of SDL2 in the render window and interactor "
"classes. The cmake option `VTK_USE_SDL2` will soon be removed. If your "
"application relies on object factory mechanism (most common usage), there is "
"nothing you need to do besides removing `VTK_USE_SDL2` from your build "
"settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/disable-sdl2-by-default.md:7
msgid "Otherwise, VTK recommends using these new webassembly classes instead."
msgstr ""

